### Test search functionality

### Search for jobs with keyword "java"
GET http://localhost:8082/api/jobs/search?keyword=java

###

### Search for jobs with keyword "developer"
GET http://localhost:8082/api/jobs/search?keyword=developer

###

### Search for jobs with keyword "bangalore"
GET http://localhost:8082/api/jobs/search?keyword=bangalore

###

### Create a job first for testing
POST http://localhost:8082/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Java Developer",
  "company": "TechCorp",
  "location": "Bangalore",
  "description": "Java development role"
}

###

### Get all jobs to verify
GET http://localhost:8082/api/jobs
